            <h2 class="section-title">Why Watches Matter</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">More than just timekeeping, watches define style, precision, and elegance.</p>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                        <h4>Timeless Legacy</h4>
                        <p>Watches symbolize heritage and craftsmanship, carrying stories across generations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                        <h4>Elevated Status</h4>
                        <p>A classic watch enhances your professional presence and personal style.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <i class="fas fa-running"></i>
                        <h4>Performance & Precision</h4>
                        <p>From fitness tracking to aviation, modern watches keep up with your lifestyle.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="brand-spotlight">
                <h3>Experience Excellence with <span class="brand-name">Time Mania</span></h3>
                <p>Your gateway to premium, stylish, and high-performance timepieces.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
